      "content": "Your years of suffering are why you view finding peace as mercy, but the human spirit often retains a profound connection to the very life that causes the agony.\nPlease speak with a specialist about palliative care, which is designed exactly for this situation by focusing on comfort rather than cure.\nIf the thought of ending this pain becomes too heavy to carry alone, reaching out to a crisis line can provide immediate, non-judgmental support when you are at your absolute lowest.",
